<div class="col-md-3"></div><div id="container" class="col-md-6"><h1 class="titletext">Concerns centered on Augmented Reality</h1>
     <br>
<p class="titletext small">
  Some Concerns about AR are about privacy and control over user data as is the concern in many emerging fields. Although augmented reality has a propensity towards education and entertainment, it can also be used for advertising and marketing.The main areas of concern come from control over data and metadata and targeted marketing, however there is also concern for the effect that this technology may have on the people using it. As the name suggests, Augmented reality should heighten a user's experience of the real world, despite that, some may argue that it actually detaches people from the real world with distractions.
</p>
<br>
<br>
